description: For sale: $899,900. You will fall in love with this well-appointed home situated on the sandy shores of Cedar Lake on a one plus acre lot, featuring an over sized attached garage plus a 31x19 boat house with rooftop deck and gazebo. This home was designed with the lake in mind featuring views from almost every room. This property gleams with pride of ownership. Many recent updates such as the kitchen, three seasons porch, sun room overlooking the lake and so much more! This home has a wonderful charm, ambiance and feel-good factor about it. It has quality accommodations, outdoor living/entertaining areas and outstanding sandy shoreline. Whether you're on the lake, relaxing around the fire or entertaining with the screened in gazebo/rooftop patio you're sure to have a good time on prestigious Cedar Lake.

For sale: $300,000. Gorgeous lot with cabin on extremely nice and clear Bass Lake, just north of Annandale. 125 feet of excellent shoreline on this lake, that boasts 15'+ water clarity. The lot is level to the lake, with southeast facing views. The vintage cabin is a great escape to the lake. It has a couple of bunk nooks & a bedroom area. The screen porch, right up next to the lake, is a great space to spend family evenings. The lot offers an excellent opportunity for a future home build. There is also a large pole building to store your lake & lawn equipment.

For sale: $324,900. Own your ADORABLE slice of heaven!! Gorgeous level Sugar Lake lakeshore with turnkey seasonal cabin! Enjoy your summer at the lake!! New siding & windows in 2009. New carpeting in 2013.  2017 updates include: new roof, bath remodel, kitchen remodel, new appliances, updated gas fireplace, rip rap Shoreline and dock decking replaced. Concrete edging added, class 5 driveway, and  improved beach area in 2018. Great fishing! Turn key and ready for you to make memories here!!

For sale: $649,900. Welcome to this one of  a kind Clearwater Lake home. This home is truly custom and has room for all of your guests! Situated on over one acre, you will love the southern exposure, minimal elevation down to the lake and natural sand shoreline. This home has a year round main house that offers four beds and two bath and then an attached seasonal guest cabin with its own kitchen, two beds and one bath and a detached seasonal guest house with a kitchen, 7th bed and 3/4 bath. This area of Clearwater Lake is known as the "Gold Coast" because of its exceptional shoreline. Clearwater Lake is almost 3200 acres featuring great fishing and is full recreation. You will never run out of things to do on this lake with a great restaurant and bait shop you can boat to along with concerts on the sandbar. Clearwater Lake is a premier lake in the west metro with great fishing. Great option for vacation rentals or just offering guests their own space. Don't miss out on this opportunity on Clearwater Lake!

description: For sale: $259,900. Wonderfully kept home with contemporary touches. Practically brand new, this home was built in 2017 by Arvola Builders and sits nicely in the Purcells Ponds neighborhood close to many of Annandale's amenities. High vaulted ceilings welcome you as you enter and extend to the upper level kitchen, dining, and living room. Many hours will be spent at the generous and extremely practical breakfast bar, while favorable weather will have you soaking up the rays and the wetland views from the 2018 cedar deck. The lower level family room invites you in to relax next to the electric, infrared fireplace. Two bedrooms, bathroom, and laundry room complete the well lit lower level. Keep your toys and vehicles toasty warm in the heated, 3 stall garage. Attractive home, great location!

description: For sale: $244,900. The beautiful stately home home has been tastefully remodeled and updated over the years but still retaining the original charm and character from yesteryear.The home offers ample square footage so plenty of room throughout the home. Home is in prime location in the town of Annandale as it backs up to middle school ball fields and local outdoor hockey rink. It is also located within walking to distance to the other schools, city park and Pleasant Lake. Possible bonus feature if buyer so chooses is the current family room has been used a studio apartment for the last several years so this could provide additional revenue to help pay the mortgage. Come check out this charming older home in the Heart of Annandale.

For sale: $925,000. WEST LAKE SYLVIA! 201 feet of fabulous lake frontage with a .9 acre lot on pristine, highly desired area lake with 18+ ft. clarity. Located in a quiet bay with west facing views for spectacular sunsets. Wooded lot with great of privacy. Hard to find sandy beach front. 3500+ sq. ft. walk out rambler in excellent condition and move-in ready. Large yard, paver fire-pit area, huge wrap around deck. Insulated detached 2+ car garage. Lots of great amenities including an indoor sauna, multi-purpose room, tons of storage. Bring your best Lake Sylvia buyers today!!

For sale: $325,000. Deeded access to Clearwater Lake makes this home a great value without the high lakeshore taxes. Nice log sided home nestled on 1+ acres of mature trees and a picturesque lot. Vaulted open floor plans with 3 bedrooms on one level, large living room with lake view. A fully finished lower level and 2 attached car garage and extra-large storage shed.

description: For sale: $349,900. Wonderful home set on the shores of Granite Lake. Walk into a spacious main level featuring vaulted ceilings and an abundance of natural light, living room warmed by a gas burning fireplace and kitchen offering fantastic lake views and walks-out to a maintenance free lakeside deck. Turn in for the night with a spacious master bedroom including a private door to the lakeside deck, walk-thru full bathroom and an additional bedroom. Entertain guests with a walk-out lower level family room and gather at the dry bar while enjoying your company. The lower level also includes a third bedroom, office, laundry room, full bathroom and storage room. Granite Lake spans across 339 acres and is located just 6 miles South of Annandale. Boat out to the grassy island or grab a pole and try your luck at fishing year round. Enjoy your summer days on Granite Lake and reminisce around a bonfire with views of your shoreline.

For sale: $293,000. Perfect combination of lake and county life mixed together with this home! Large 3 acre lot with deeded access to Cedar Lake. This home features 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, multiple living areas and main level laundry. Heated 2 stall garage and an extra storage shed for all the outdoor toys. The deck and patio areas have great views of the mature trees in the backyard. Deeded access is located just down the street!

description: For sale: $189,900. Welcome to this one-of-a-kind turn of the century home set in the Heart of the Lakes. Entertain with a spacious main level offering a large kitchen, dining room that opens to the living room both dripping with natural light and a master suite complete with a walk-thru three-quarter bathroom. Retreat for the night in an upper level offering three bedrooms and a full bathroom. Spread out with even more space in the lower level family room including a gas fireplace and leading to a half bathroom and many storage areas. The home is complete with a detached garage, storage shed and deck. Relax on your covered front porch and enjoy the heart of Annandale. Located just off the Annandale's Historic 4th of July parade route this home is situated a stone's throw from the fantastic city park offering a beach area, boat landing, playground, fishing pier and softball field.

For sale: $329,000. Excellent location! Great view of Cedar Lake, close to town. Beautiful 4.5 acre lot w/ woods & irrigated gardens. Your own orchard featuring apples trees, pear trees, cherry trees, strawberry plants, and more. Six bedroom home, ready for your family. 3 bedrooms on the main floor, 3 on the lower w/o level. Nice wood burning fireplace, large rooms, huge 4 season sun room. Watch an abundance of wildlife in your back yard. Association access to Cedar Lake. Great home in the country, but less than 5 minutes to town.

For sale: $470,000. Cedar Lake.  Level lot with excellent frontage on .7 acre. Fabulous views. 2 Bed/2 bath rambler. Finished basement. Open floor plan with vaulted ceilings and wall of windows facing the lake. Lots of lakeside deck space and a screened gazebo. Large garage on the back lot. Roadside storage shed and lakeside shed. Great condition, year round home.

Recently sold: $239,900. Quality built home by local builder on large walk-out lot with a small pond, tree house, and tree swing in the backyard with wetland to the rear for privacy.

description:
Recently sold: $375,000. MAIN LEVEL 

Kitchen 
The kitchen showcases an ample amount of built-in cabinetry, plenty of counter space, beautiful tiled floors, and is open to the rest of the main floor. 

Living Room
The living room is large and bright with an abundance of natural light and stunning lakeshore views. It has a fireplace with built-ins, carpet, plenty of space for entertaining and a great open floor plan. 

Informal Dining
The informal Dining room is bright and open with tiled flooring, open to the entire first floor and has a beautiful chandelier.

4 Season Porch
Stunning 4 season porch covered in knotty pine from top to bottom with vaulted ceilings and a ceiling fan. Surrounded with views of Sugar Lake. This room is set up for a theatre room with a projector screen, projector, and speakers. Walk out the sliding glass door to enjoy your 30x12 deck, the perfect place for a BBQ or to sit and enjoy the beautiful lake. 

Master Bedroom
The master suite is large and has a sliding glass door leading to the deck with lakeside views. It has carpet, ceiling fan, and a private ½ bathroom. 

Bedroom 2 
The second main floor bedroom is great in size with carpet and adjacent to a full bath.

Laundry 
The walk thru laundry room is located on the main floor with tons of cupboard storage, laundry sink, and can also be used as a mudroom. Washer and Dryer are sold with the property.

LOWER LEVEL

Family Room 
The family room in the lower level is huge with carpeted floors and is adjacent to the lower level bedrooms. 

Bedrooms 3 & 4
The two lower level bedrooms are large with nice sized closets, egress windows, and carpeted floors. Conveniently located next to a full-size bathroom. 

Workshop
This 24 x 09 space in the lower level is the perfect for a workshop or storage.

SPECIAL FEATURES:
-	100+ ft of Lakeshore Frontage on Sugar Lake
-	Sandy Shoreline
-	Optional Sugar Lake Association - $50/Year
-	Boat House 18 x 10
-	In-Ground Sprinkler System
-	Fully Wood Fenced Backyard
-	Very Well Maintained
-	Oversized 2 Car Garage
-	Storage Shed 12 x 10
-	Lifetime Warranty on 7 Windows ? Transfers to New Buyer
-	Award Winning School District

Does Not Stay: 
-	Dog Kennel
-	Wine Fridge on Upper Level
-	Fridges/Freezer in Basement Workshop Room
-	All Bedroom Curtains
-	Docks & Lifts (negotiable)
